		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Those are all options relating to your display though. Stuff that's nowadays handled by the console's own system settings.<br />The options introduced in Star Ocean 4 affects how the game is rendered on the PS4's own hardware, and has nothing to do with differences on your TV.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


